      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so hopeless though. like no matter who i talk to, the debt is still there and the exams are still coming. i look at my life and i just don't see anything worth the struggle anymore. it feels like everyone would actually be better off if i just wasn't around to let them down. it would just be peaceful, you know? just silence.",
